No. 09-7909. Norma Cristina Drummond de Johnson, Petitioner v. Eric H. Holder, Jr., Attorney General. 560 U.S. 919, 130 S. Ct. 3273,

176 L. Ed. 2d 1210,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 4095. May 17, 2010.

Petition for writ of cer-tiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Second Circuit denied.

Same case below, 564 F.3d 95.
